{
  "_note": "Phase-1 Styling Presets for the PayForItUK round-trip. No preset import file/UI yet (contract gap, roadmap #2) — this is the payload to apply per-key to wp_option `fw_ext_settings_options:shortcodes` via the future importer / update_option / WP-CLI. Shapes mirror framework/includes/presets/*.php defaults (all verified against the default fns).",
  "_apply_to_option": "fw_ext_settings_options:shortcodes",
