    "_button_sizes": "Use plugin defaults (xl/lg/md/sm/xs) — radii 10/8/6/5/3 match the design's button radii. No override needed.",
    "_border_presets": "Use plugin defaults — 'Card' (.colb-card: radius 8, light-gray hairline, soft shadow, lifts on hover) maps the .trust-pillar/.card/.faq/.trust-block look now that 'light-gray' is in the palette. 'Hover Lift' (.colb-hover-lift) maps the .method-tile/.what-pay-row hover-to-primary. No override needed."
